\sum_{k=0}^{2n}\binom{2n}k=\sum_{k=0}^\infty\binom{2n}k=\sum_{k=0}^\infty\binom{2n+1}{2k+1}=\sum_{k=0}^n\binom{2n+1}{2k+1}
2^{2n+1}=2\cdot 4^n
\sum_{k=0}^n {2n+1 \choose 2k}
\sum_{k=0}^n {2n+1 \choose 2k}=\sum_{k=0}^n{2n+1 \choose 2n+1-2k}=\sum_{k=0}^n{2n+1 \choose 2k+1}.
